{{TagLine|AC2400 Dual Band Smart Wi-Fi Router}} :{{ProductPage|https://quantum.humaxdigital.com/product/quantum-t9/}} The Test Report 1 FCC document indicates that this FCC ID may also cover the T5 :and T7 models with the number of antennas (and streams) reduced as follows: *[[Humax Quantum T5]]: 2x2 2.4GHz, 3x3 5GHz ([[Lantiq#WAVE500|WAVE500]] Series) *[[Humax Quantum T7]]: 3x3 2.4GHz, 3x3 5GHz ([[Lantiq#WAVE500|WAVE500]] Series) {{FCC ST|04/15/2018|indexme.}} ===Specifications=== :[http://item.gmarket.co.kr/Item?goodscode=1171424904 ''Humax Quantum T9'' on '''GMarket'''] *CPU: [[Intel (Lantiq)]] PXB4395 @1.6GHz (GRX350 Dual Core) *Flash: 256MB (NAND), RAM: 512MB (DDR3), USB: USB 3.0 *WLAN: [[Lantiq (Intel)]] [[Lantiq#WAVE500|WAVE500]] Series (Wave2, MU-MIMO) :2.4GHz: [[Lantiq (Intel)]] PSB 83513M (3T3R 802.11bgn) :5GHz: [[Lantiq (Intel)]] PSB 83524M (4T4R 802.11an/ac) *Ports: 1x WAN GbE, 2x LAN GbE; 1x USB 3.0; *Power Adapter: DC 12V/2.5A *Dimensions: 105x105x185 mm (WxDxH) *Weight: 835g ===See also=== :[https://quantum.humaxdigital.com/product/ Humax Quantum Products] *[[Humax Quantum T5]] - ''AC1700 High Performance Wi-Fi Router'' :CPU: Intel ''Hexa'' @1.6GHz (dual-core), 256MB Flash/512MB RAM *[[Humax Quantum T5x]] - ''AC1700 High Performance Wi-Fi Router'' :CPU: Intel ''Hexa'' @1.6GHz (dual-core), 256MB Flash/512MB RAM *[[Humax Quantum T7]] - ''AC1900 High Performance Wi-Fi Router'' :CPU: Intel ''Hexa'' @1.6GHz (dual-core), 256MB Flash/512MB RAM *[[Humax Quantum T7x]] - ''AC1700 High Performance Wi-Fi Router'' :CPU: Intel ''Hexa'' @1.6GHz (dual-core), 256MB Flash/512MB RAM *[[Humax Quantum T9]] - ''AC2400 High Performance Wi-Fi Router'' :CPU: Intel ''Hexa'' @1.6GHz (dual-core), 256MB Flash/512MB RAM *[[Humax Quantum T9x]] - ''AC2400 High Performance Wi-Fi Router'' :CPU: Intel ''Hexa'' @1.6GHz (dual-core), 256MB Flash/512MB RAM __NOTOC__
